graph TB
    subgraph 数据输入层
        CREDIT[信用卡]
        LOAN[消费贷]
        MORTGAGE[房贷]
        CARLOAN[车贷]
    end

    subgraph 健康评估引擎
        DTI[债务收入比]
        PAYMENT[还款比]
        INTEREST[利息分析]
        LEVEL[健康等级]
    end

    subgraph 还款策略
        SNOWBALL[雪球法]
        AVALANCHE[雪崩法]
        HYBRID[混合策略]
        PRIORITY[优先级排序]
    end

    subgraph 计划生成
        MIN_PAY[最低还款]
        EXTRA[额外还款分配]
        SCHEDULE[还款计划]
        SIMULATE[模拟计算]
    end

    subgraph 利息追踪
        MONTHLY[月利息计算]
        TOTAL[累计利息]
        COMPARE[策略对比]
        SAVE[节省潜力]
    end

    subgraph 动态调整
        INCOME_CHG[收入变化]
        DEBT_CHG[债务变化]
        ADJUST[计划调整]
        ALERT[预警通知]
    end

    CREDIT --> DTI
    LOAN --> DTI
    MORTGAGE --> DTI
    CARLOAN --> DTI

    DTI --> PAYMENT
    PAYMENT --> INTEREST
    INTEREST --> LEVEL

    LEVEL --> SNOWBALL
    LEVEL --> AVALANCHE
    LEVEL --> HYBRID
    SNOWBALL --> PRIORITY
    AVALANCHE --> PRIORITY
    HYBRID --> PRIORITY

    PRIORITY --> MIN_PAY
    MIN_PAY --> EXTRA
    EXTRA --> SCHEDULE
    SCHEDULE --> SIMULATE

    SIMULATE --> MONTHLY
    MONTHLY --> TOTAL
    TOTAL --> COMPARE
    COMPARE --> SAVE

    SCHEDULE --> INCOME_CHG
    INCOME_CHG --> DEBT_CHG
    DEBT_CHG --> ADJUST
    ADJUST --> ALERT

